{
  "stem": "18626.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When the people were shot, their clothes were taken in from the fortress, then the Jewish Committee knew that anytime they take out people, they are going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But a lot of times they took out people not to be killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took people in different sections, in different parts of Lithuania, for slave labor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Like they took people to Kadan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They took people to other little villages and states in Lithuania to do labor work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But when they took out these people, it was a different atmosphere, then when they took out people to kill.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When they took people to kill, the SS, the way they acted was in a different manner.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "A lot of them were drunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "A lot of them knew that these 1,500 people are going to be dead in five or six hours, like cattle in a slaughter house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they treated these people, you know, with the rifle butts over the heads, over the shoulders.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "March fast!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] It was a different type of treatment then people go to-- when they took people out for labor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they figured, no use crippling the people when they take them to labor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're not going to be able to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when the commanders, the Gestapo came, and they knew already that these type people are going to-- these people are going to be killed, these people were treated like cattle to a slaughterhouse.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the committee, the Jewish Committee knew most of the time already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they didn't have no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Elkes couldn't say, kill me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm not going to give out no more Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they would find another leader, a Jewish man who wants to save his life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It couldn't help.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's nothing against the Jewish Committee.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
